# Cloudflare Workers static-assets redirects. Copied verbatim from
# `public/` to `dist/` by Vite at build time; Cloudflare evaluates
# these BEFORE the SPA fallback, so a JS-less crawler or AI agent
# fetching a legacy URL gets a real 301 to the canonical route
# instead of a 200 SPA shell (Codex #1309 r9).
#
# /buy-vpfi → /vpfi: the marketing page moved when the fixed-rate
# sale was removed (#712). The React-router alias (App.tsx
# `path="buy-vpfi"`) stays for client-side navigations; these rules
# cover direct fetches. Query strings carry over automatically;
# fragments are preserved by the browser across a 301.
#
# Locale list mirrors LOCALES in scripts/seo-routes.mjs — keep in
# sync when a translated locale is added.

/buy-vpfi /vpfi 301
/es/buy-vpfi /es/vpfi 301
/fr/buy-vpfi /fr/vpfi 301
/de/buy-vpfi /de/vpfi 301
/ja/buy-vpfi /ja/vpfi 301
/zh/buy-vpfi /zh/vpfi 301
/hi/buy-vpfi /hi/vpfi 301
/ar/buy-vpfi /ar/vpfi 301
/ta/buy-vpfi /ta/vpfi 301
/ko/buy-vpfi /ko/vpfi 301
